Photo mosaic
------------

ABOUT

Install the server dependencies with setup.sh, then run the server with start.sh.  Those scripts assume a Mac environment, but are trivial enough to replicate on Linux if required.

SOURCES

Uploading a file:

https://developer.mozilla.org/en/docs/Using_files_from_web_applications

Slicing the image:

https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/getImageData

Calculating the average colour:

https://developer.mozilla.org/en/docs/Web/API/ImageData

https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Uint8ClampedArray

https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/Reduce

Converting RGB to HEX:

http://stackoverflow.com/questions/5623838/rgb-to-hex-and-hex-to-rgb